@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}


<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        h1, h2, h3 {
            color: #007BFF;
            text-align: center;
        }
        p {
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            text-align: justify;
        }
        .features {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .features ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .features li {
                background: #BA6FF7;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 5px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .cta {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .cta a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 20px;
                background: #B218F2;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 18px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .cta a:hover {
                    background: #B218F2;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <h2>Revolutionizing Transportation Management</h2>
        <p>Welcome to <strong>Transport Module</strong>, your ultimate solution for modern and efficient transportation management. We are committed to transforming the way businesses and individuals handle transportation logistics with our advanced, user-friendly, and secure platform.</p>

        <h3>Who We Are</h3>
        <p>At <strong>Transport Module</strong>, we believe in leveraging technology to simplify and optimize transportation operations. Whether it's <strong>booking, billing management, route planning, payment integration, real-time schedules, or personalized user profiles</strong>, our platform is designed to meet diverse transportation needs with efficiency, reliability, and security.</p>

        <h3>Why Choose Us?</h3>
        <div class="features">
            <ul>
                <li>✔ Comprehensive Features</li>
                <li>✔ User-Friendly Interface</li>
                <li>✔ Secure & Reliable</li>
                <li>✔ Scalability & Flexibility</li>
                <li>✔ Dedicated Support</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <h3>Join Us in Shaping the Future of Transportation</h3>
        <p>At <strong>Transport Module</strong>, we are constantly evolving to meet the changing demands of the transportation industry. Our innovative approach ensures that businesses and individuals have access to cutting-edge technology for seamless transport operations.</p>

        <div class="cta">
            <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">🚀 Get Started Today!</a>
        </div>

    </div>
</body>
</html>
